{"nodes": [{"id": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design", "label": "Issue Details Rail Progressive Disclosure Design Spec", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-08-issue-details-rail-progressive-disclosure-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design_railfields_registry", "label": "RAIL_FIELDS Descriptor Registry", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-08-issue-details-rail-progressive-disclosure-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Metadata-only registry: the rail's fields render heterogeneous bespoke markup, and forcing them behind one uniform component contract is not worth it \u2014 the registry owns visibility/ordering/menu/removal, rendering stays in the template. A future field = one RAIL_FIELDS entry + one template block. Built to scale to the full GitLab attribute set rather than hand-maintained per-field branches."}, {"id": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design_userailfields", "label": "useRailFields Visibility Composable", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-08-issue-details-rail-progressive-disclosure-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "revealed/removed are transient this-session intent, cleared on save and cancel only \u2014 nothing new persists to GitLab or localStorage."}, {"id": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design_visibility_state_machine", "label": "Rail Field Visibility State Machine", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-08-issue-details-rail-progressive-disclosure-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Visibility is fully derived from four inputs (original populated, draft populated, revealed set, removed set) \u2014 no per-field UI flags scattered around the component. Pinned fields (Status, Labels, Assignees) anchor every issue and never enter the Add menu; booleans ride the same model with isPopulated = flag===true."}], "edges": [{"source": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design", "target": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design_railfields_registry", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-08-issue-details-rail-progressive-disclosure-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design", "target": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design_userailfields", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-08-issue-details-rail-progressive-disclosure-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design", "target": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design_visibility_state_machine", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-08-issue-details-rail-progressive-disclosure-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design_userailfields", "target": "specs_2026_06_08_issue_details_rail_progressive_disclosure_design_railfields_registry", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-08-issue-details-rail-progressive-disclosure-d